properties.headline: Air Quality Alert issued January 22 at 2:20PM EST by NWS Gray ME
properties.description:
The New Hampshire Department of Environmental Services has issued
an air quality action day for the following counties...

Cheshire.

THE NEW HAMPSHIRE DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL SERVICES IS PREDICTING
UNHEALTHY AIR QUALITY FOR SENSITIVE GROUPS IN CHESHIRE COUNTY,
ESPECIALLY POPULATED VALLEY AREAS, WEDNESDAY EVENING THROUGH
SATURDAY. CHILDREN, OLDER ADULTS, OR ANYONE WITH HEART OR LUNG
DISEASE WHO ARE IN THESE AREAS SHOULD LIMIT PROLONGED EXERTION.

NWSheadline: Air quality alert is in effect from 10 AM Wednesday until 10 PM Saturday
